<div class="thank-you-container" style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem">
  <h1>Thank You!</h1>
  <p>
    Your order has been placed successfully and our team will reach out to you
    soon via email.
  </p>
  <p>If you'd like to review your order, please click the link below:</p>
  <a
    href="/order/<%= orderId %>"
    class="btn"
    style="
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
    "
  >
    Review Your Order
  </a>
</div>